{"type":null,"faqId":37057,"title":"手环如何恢复出厂设置？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.9111111in 1.25in 1.0in 1.25in;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{font-family:宋体;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>手环和手机通过蓝牙正常连接时，在华为穿戴APP中点击左上角设置图标，点击“恢复出厂设置”手环将恢复出厂设置。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>说明：手环恢复出厂设置后，手环上的运动、睡眠和时间数据都会清零，再次使用时需要重新配对连接手机。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>如手环无法登陆APP或者死机、卡机时，</span><span class=\"s1\">请连接充电器并同时长按侧键30秒以上后再松手，尝试硬件复位，看是否可以开机</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":203,"faqType":"兼容与支持","useful":0,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2221","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-System-Requirements-Support","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1440750140000,"seriesProductName":"B2","visitedTimes":351,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"华为手环,B2,恢复出厂设置","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}